        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-blue-200 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Kualitas</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Komitmen pada standar kualitas tertinggi dalam setiap project yang kami kerjakan, 
            dari material hingga finishing.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-green-200 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Inovasi</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Terus mengadopsi teknologi terbaru dan mengembangkan metode kerja yang lebih 
            efisien dan efektif.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-purple-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-purple-200 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Integritas</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Transparansi, kejujuran, dan profesionalisme dalam setiap interaksi dengan 
            klien dan partner bisnis.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center group">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 group-hover:bg-orange-200 transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Kepuasan Pelanggan</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Mengutamakan kepuasan dan kepercayaan pelanggan melalui pelayanan yang 
            responsif dan solusi yang tepat.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Our Team -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="heading-lg text-gray-900 mb-6">Tim Ahli Kami</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Tim profesional berpengalaman yang siap memberikan solusi terbaik untuk setiap kebutuhan laser cutting Anda.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <img 
            src="/team-director.webp"
            alt="Direktur LaserCut Pro"
            class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            width="96"
            height="96"
          />
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Budi Santoso</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-600 font-medium mb-3">Direktur & Founder</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            15+ tahun pengalaman di industri manufaktur dan teknologi laser cutting. 
            Visionaris di balik inovasi dan pertumbuhan LaserCut Pro.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <img 
            src="/team-technical.webp"
            alt="Technical Manager LaserCut Pro"
            class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            width="96"
            height="96"
          />
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Ahmad Rizki</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-600 font-medium mb-3">Technical Manager</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Ahli teknis dengan sertifikasi internasional dalam operasi dan maintenance 
            mesin laser cutting berbagai jenis.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <img 
            src="/team-design.webp"
            alt="Design Specialist LaserCut Pro"
            class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            width="96"
            height="96"
          />
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sari Dewi</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-600 font-medium mb-3">Design Specialist</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Spesialis design dan CAD dengan keahlian dalam optimasi file untuk 
            berbagai jenis material dan aplikasi cutting.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 text-center hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
          <img 
            src="/team-quality.webp"
            alt="Quality Control LaserCut Pro"
            class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
            width="96"
            height="96"
          />
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Dedi Kurniawan</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-600 font-medium mb-3">Quality Control</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Bertanggung jawab memastikan setiap hasil cutting memenuhi standar 
            kualitas tinggi sebelum diserahkan kepada klien.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Certifications & Awards -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="heading-lg text-gray-900 mb-6">Sertifikat & Penghargaan</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Pengakuan atas komitmen kami terhadap kualitas, keamanan, dan standar industri internasional.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-blue-100 rounded-xl p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
